143
00:10:34,022 --> 00:10:35,922
Penuh dengan goresan.

144
00:10:37,222 --> 00:10:39,822
Kurasa dia bukan orang yang baik.

145
00:10:40,922 --> 00:10:41,922
Oh, hei.

146
00:10:45,822 --> 00:10:47,622
Ibu.

147
00:10:47,622 --> 00:10:49,622
Dia gemetar?

148
00:10:49,622 --> 00:10:51,522
Gemetaran itu...

149
00:10:51,522 --> 00:10:54,022
