169
00:11:52,322 --> 00:11:54,222
Aku takkan memaafkannya.

170
00:11:54,222 --> 00:11:59,222
Aku takkan memaafkan pria itu!

171
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:10,260
Begitu. Jadi seperti itu.

172
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:14,060
Jika deduksiku benar, pria itu adalah...

173
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:16,060
Dari cara dia bicara bayi,

174
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:19,560
